description: The Soul Food Café Express is a mobile eatery serving the streets of Las vegas. Their menu offers a collection of traditional southern food with a common theme: Healthy, Flavorful, and Familiar. Their goal is to create satisfying, wholesome, nutritious food. With the increased awareness of nutritional food options, Soul Food Cafe Express is providing a healthy alternative to good old fashioned Soul Food!
name: Soul Food Cafe Express
